{"tid":270908,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"9-10月想搵人一齊攀登雲南麗江既哈巴雪山，７日行程表與費用，有冇人JOIN?","createTime":"2017-06-04T15:44:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-06T11:31:39.000Z","uid":121126,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"583d380d38da5977d5595003dcc0dca3954a29cc","tid":270908,"uid":121126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:44:20.000Z","msg":"其實都係受有位巴打既POST既影響所以想試下登雪山，打第由容易入手先，所以先試入門級雪山,爬過雪山緊係順便去麗江感受下氣氛喇，本身約左ＦＤ，但佢突然唔去得，所以想搵人一齊去，本人27歲，希望搵到既旅伴係３０歲以內，因為唔想太大會有代溝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n哈巴雪山，意為「金子之花朵」，主峰海拔 5396 米，為雲南省境內第四高峰<br />\n，因緯度低，氣候相對較溫和，且攀登周期短，岩石地帶沒有太難地形，雪線以上地形簡單，沒有明顯冰裂縫，一直是雲南登山愛好者首選的入門級山峰，稱為「雲南的玉珠峰」<br />\n<br />\n巴哈雪山圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.imi.buzz/images/2017/06/04/551.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.imi.buzz%2Fimages%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F551.jpg&h=acd06902&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.imi.buzz/images/2017/06/04/1618075z57cn344t3qici5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.imi.buzz%2Fimages%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F1618075z57cn344t3qici5.jpg&h=6174ebdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.imi.buzz/images/2017/06/04/wKgB6lSAjBuAE5aZAAhRYz4QMXI25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.imi.buzz%2Fimages%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2FwKgB6lSAjBuAE5aZAAhRYz4QMXI25.jpg&h=41bfc85c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.imi.buzz/images/2017/06/04/wKgBpVURHtWAT0sOAAKhozZxlaQ88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.imi.buzz%2Fimages%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2FwKgBpVURHtWAT0sOAAKhozZxlaQ88.jpg&h=0640918e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.imi.buzz/images/2017/06/04/DSC06922.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.imi.buzz%2Fimages%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2FDSC06922.jpg&h=88b6b344&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n麗江<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.imi.buzz/images/2017/06/04/1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.imi.buzz%2Fimages%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F1.jpg&h=be8350db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.imi.buzz/images/2017/06/04/2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.imi.buzz%2Fimages%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F2.jpg&h=300c5738&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.imi.buzz/images/2017/06/04/3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.imi.buzz%2Fimages%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F3.jpg&h=fca657a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.imi.buzz/images/2017/06/04/4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.imi.buzz%2Fimages%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F4.jpg&h=f6635ebf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.imi.buzz/images/2017/06/04/5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.imi.buzz%2Fimages%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F5.jpg&h=3ac95e21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.imi.buzz/images/2017/06/04/6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.imi.buzz%2Fimages%2F2017%2F06%2F04%2F6.jpg&h=b44659c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好喇，回正題<br />\n<br />\n大約去7日,應該係星期一早上出發，星期日中午返黎，總行程大約２－４人<br />\n<br />\n行程1:<br />\n星期一早上香港飛昆明，到中午轉機去麗江再到巴哈村<br />\n星期二巴哈村上哈巴雪山大本營，適應一日<br />\n星期三大本營衝上峰頂，再落巴哈村回麗江<br />\n星期四麗江之行<br />\n星期五麗江之行<br />\n星期六麗江回昆明<br />\n星期日昆明飛香港<br />\n<br />\n行程1:費用<br />\n香港昆明來回機票  900-1000<br />\n麗江昆明來回機票  900<br />\n7天交通費    500<br />\n麗江三天住宿(基本-豪華) 1000-1600<br />\n昆明一天住宿 250<br />\n7日食玩洗用  2000-2500<br />\n登雪山費用 (包括星期一和二的食宿，1對1雪山協助，冰爪冰鎬雪鏡等裝備租用，營地清潔費)  2000<br />\n每人總數 7500-9000<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行程2:<br />\n星期一早上香港飛昆明，到中午轉機去麗江再到巴哈村<br />\n星期二巴哈村上哈巴雪山大本營，適應一日<br />\n星期三大本營衝上峰頂，再落巴哈村回麗江<br />\n星期四各自安排<br />\n星期五各自安排<br />\n星期六麗江回昆明-各自行程<br />\n星期日昆明飛香港<br />\n<br />\n行程2:費用<br />\n香港昆明來回機票  900-1000<br />\n麗江昆明來回機票  900<br />\n7天交通費    500<br />\n登雪山費用 (包括星期一和二的食宿，1對1雪山協助，冰爪冰鎬雪鏡等裝備租用，營地清潔費)2000<br />\n各自安排住宿和食玩費用 ????<br />\n<br />\n每人總數基本費用 4300+????<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上已經價錢轉左HKD"},{"pid":"1f2abb7b1f147e3399e74f52dd6adcb90d44eea1","tid":270908,"uid":121126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T16:02:11.000Z","msg":"有意既可以加我<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ColumbiaGD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FColumbiaGD&d=Y5GMY9%2FVJpBehHhQiuB7rfM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=c3903973\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ColumbiaGD</a>"},{"pid":"013cca525eef13031f176ee8b36052e5d6f53d96","tid":270908,"uid":121126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T01:30:33.000Z","msg":"推👍🏻"},{"pid":"d7f35e8a1ef7761c08d61ab03fc76b6db909af95","tid":270908,"uid":121126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T03:54:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b43e3d6f6716f4fc81033f883b5425b44423f8b","tid":270908,"uid":82715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T03:58:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c6f68501561726bfa6b968717eae55b06b874f6b","tid":270908,"uid":79035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T04:08:46.000Z","msg":"昆明我呀媽鄉下<br />\n麗江幾年前去過 因為同親戚去 係山腳留咗陣就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n留名睇detail"},{"pid":"51fe5b3405fdcd55d8b34936edaa53815c4e51a1","tid":270908,"uid":14511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T04:13:49.000Z","msg":"麗江第2幅係瀘沽湖黎"},{"pid":"af623aae9a274dc22395b4e2e5b26866f015fd11","tid":270908,"uid":121126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T04:52:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我打算九月去爬EBC, 有興趣可以都TELGARM 我 @rayyau921</blockquote><br />\n得你一個人？"},{"pid":"f2cac1e60c5f9c123b99bcbff4744954731c851f","tid":270908,"uid":121126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T04:53:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>麗江第2幅係瀘沽湖黎</blockquote><br />\nD圖我係google搵<img src=\"/a